><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Zwraca nazwę węzła jako ciąg znaków.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><i>nazwa</i> = element.nodeName\n</pre>\n<p>\n <i>\n  nazwa</i>\n to ciąg znaków reprezentujący nazwę bieżącego elementu. <code>nodeName</code> to atrybut tylko do odczytu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniżej przedstawione są wartości zwracane dla różnych typów węzłów:</p>\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th class=\"header\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Interfejs</th>\n   <th class=\"header\" style=\"text-align: center;\">nodeName</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/Attr\">Attr</a></td>\n   <td>tak samo jak <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/Attr.name\">Attr.name</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/CDATASection\">CDATASection</a></td>\n   <td>\"#cdata-section\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/Comment\">Comment</a></td>\n   <td>\"#comment\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/Document\">Document</a></td>\n   <td>\"#document\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/DocumentFragment\">DocumentFragment</a></td>\n   <td>\"#document-fragment\"</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/DocumentType\">DocumentType</a></td>\n   <td>tak samo jak <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/DocumentType.name\">DocumentType.name</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/Element\">Element</a></td>\n   <td>tak samo jak <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/element.tagName\">Element.tagName</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/Entity\">Entity</a></td>\n   <td>nazwa encji</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/EntityReference\">EntityReference</a></td>\n   <td>nazwa refernecji do encji</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/Notation\">Notation</a></td>\n   <td>nazwa notacji</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"pl/DOM/ProcessingInstruction\">ProcessingInstruction</a></td>\n   <td>tak samo jak <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/ProcessingInstruction.target\">ProcessingInstruction.target</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Text</td>\n   <td>\"#text\"</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Dane są poniższe znaczniki</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;div id=\"d1\"&gt;hello world&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"text\" id=\"t\"/&gt;\n</pre>\n<p>i taki skrypt:</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var div1 = document.getElementById(\"d1\");\nvar poleTekstowe = document.getElementById(\"t\");\npoleTekstowe.value = div1.nodeName;\n</pre>\n<p>W XHTML-u (lub innym formacie XML) wartość pola tekstowego to \"div\". W HTML wartość ta to \"DIV\".</p>\n<p>Zauważ, że można było użyć właściwości <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/element.tagName\">tagName</a></code>, ponieważ dla elementów <code>nodeName</code> ma taką samą wartość jak <code>tagName</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-F68D095\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM Level 2 Core: nodeName</a></p>\n<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-F68D095\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM Level 3 Core: nodeName</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Zwraca nazwę węzła jako ciąg znaków.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element.nodeName","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.nodeName","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Node.nodeName","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/node/nodename","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/node/nodename/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName","title":"element.nodeName"}],"pageTitle":"element.nodeName - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}